  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Monchling and hatch into the world not able to do too much.. But not to worry! You can consume creatures that have been distorted by a mysterious power and acquire abilities to help you through the journey ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/a3d083c813bca6638f348f898fce7cb8.poster.avif?t=1747257365\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/a3d083c813bca6638f348f898fce7cb8.webm?t=1747257365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/a3d083c813bca6638f348f898fce7cb8.mp4?t=1747257365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monch a variety of creatures to gain their abilities. Use them to navigate and interact with the world in new ways as you unlock and upgrade them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax while solving light puzzles and exploring a hand crafted open world full of chill vibes at your own pace. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help out the cute locals as they try to deal with a curious infestation, and discover the ancient secrets hidden within this quaint world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is full of things to collect as you go so keep your eyes peeled!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/1c191e75a31c9c7f6e1585bf63e8aa44.poster.avif?t=1747257365\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/1c191e75a31c9c7f6e1585bf63e8aa44.webm?t=1747257365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/1c191e75a31c9c7f6e1585bf63e8aa44.mp4?t=1747257365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Monchling and hatch into the world not able to do too much.. But not to worry! You can consume creatures that have been distorted by a mysterious power and acquire abilities to help you through the journey ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/a3d083c813bca6638f348f898fce7cb8.poster.avif?t=1747257365\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/a3d083c813bca6638f348f898fce7cb8.webm?t=1747257365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/a3d083c813bca6638f348f898fce7cb8.mp4?t=1747257365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monch a variety of creatures to gain their abilities. Use them to navigate and interact with the world in new ways as you unlock and upgrade them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax while solving light puzzles and exploring a hand crafted open world full of chill vibes at your own pace. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help out the cute locals as they try to deal with a curious infestation, and discover the ancient secrets hidden within this quaint world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is full of things to collect as you go so keep your eyes peeled!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079990/extras/1c191e75a31c9c7f6e1585bf63e8aa44.poster.avif?t=1747257365\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steam